race.description: Happy 80Th Jimmy Madden Showcase Super Mdn Plate
race.comment: DANCING MAN (2) lacks early speed so his two efforts this prep in 1000m dashes have had merit. Enjoys a cosy run from the inside draw today and over an extra furlong will be tough to hold out. SACRED INFERNO (11) has been beaten under a length in his two runs to date, the latest over today's trip at Wagga Riverside where he drove hard late. Perfectly drawn and the winkers go on so a breakthrough win will not surprise. HOLY HELL (6) returns from a nine-month spell. Showed ability in the maiden prep including a competitive effort over a mile in town. Needs further but while fresh can sneak into the finish. THE EYES HAVE IT (8) chalked up another minor placing last start when second-up. Cherry ripe and a must for exotics punters. ELASAND (13) has shown promise in her two runs to date. Steps up a little in trip now and should be right in the finish again.
